arts]]|page=|date=2006|isbn=4-87131-077-9}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Netherlands|type=single|title=Like a Prayer|artist=Madonna|award=Platinum|relyear=1989|certref=<ref name=dutchyear/>|accessdate=May 2, 2013}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=New Zealand|type=single|title=Like a Prayer|artist=Madonna|award=Gold|relyear=1989|certyear=1989|id=3358|accessdate=May 18, 2016|recent=website}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Spain|type=single|title=Like a Prayer|artist=Madonna|award=Gold|relyear=1989|certref=<ref name=spain/>|accessdate=May 2, 2013}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Sweden|type=single|artist=Madonna|title=Like a Prayer|award=Platinum|relyear=1989|certyear=1989|accessdate=May 2, 2013}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Switzerland|type=single|artist=Madonna|title=Like a Prayer|award=Gold|relyear=1989|certyear=1989|accessdate=May 2, 2013}}\n|-\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United Kingdom|type=single|title=Like a Prayer|artist=Madonna|award=Gold|relyear=1989|salesamount=850,500|salesref=<ref name=\"uksales\">{{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/madonnas-lead-singles-ranked__26119/|title=Madonna's lead singles ranked |last=Myers|first=Justin|date=April 24, 2019|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=April 24, 2019}}</ref>|refname=\"bpi\"|accessdate=June 4, 2015}}\n|-\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United States|type=single|title=Like a Prayer|artist=Madonna|award=Platinum|relyear=1989|certyear=1989|refname=\"riaa\"|accessdate=May 2, 2013}}\n|-\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United States| title=Like a Prayer | artist=Madonna |type=single|nocert=yes|note=Digital downloads|relyear=1998|salesref=<ref name=\"ussales\"/>|salesamount=1,100,000}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom|streaming=true}}\n\n==See also==\n{{Wikipedia books|Like a Prayer}}\n{{div col|colwidth=30em}}\n*[[List of best-selling singles]]\n*[[List of number-one singles in Australia during the 1980s|List of number-one singles o