60408172518/http://www.ausbt.com.au/files/A330neo%20Launch%20Presentation.pdf | archivedate=8 April 2016 | url-status=dead | work=ausbt.com.au}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"FG140714\">{{cite news | url=http://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/farnborough-airbus-lays-out-a330neo-specifications-401421 | title=Farnborough: Airbus lays out A330neo specifications | publisher=[[flightglobal]] | work=flightglobal.com | date=14 July 2014 | last=Kaminski-Morrow | first=David}}</ref>\n<ref name=AW140714>{{cite news |author=Jens Flottau |title= Defining priorities |work= Aviation Week and Space Technology |date= 14 July 2014 |page= 70 |url= http://aviationweek.com/awin-only/airbus-mulls-a330neo-launch-options-a350a380}}{{paywall}}</ref>\n<ref name=AW140716>{{cite news |url= http://aviationweek.com/farnborough-2014/leahy-sees-ten-month-airbus-a330neo-rate |title= Leahy Sees Ten Per Month Airbus A330neo Rate |work= Aviation Week |date= 16 July 2014}}</ref>\n<ref name=WSJ140716>{{cite news |url= https://www.wsj.com/articles/aircraft-makers-narrow-engine-options-1405457174 |last=Wall|first=Robert|first2=Jon|last2=Ostrower|first3=Rory|last3=Jones|title= Aircraft makers curb engine choices |work= Wall Street Journal |date= 16 July 2014 |page= B3|url-access=subscription}}</ref>\n<ref name=AW140721>{{cite web |url= http://aviationweek.com/commercial-aviation/airbus-more-1000-orders-coming-a330neo |title= Airbus: More Than 1,000 Orders Coming For A330neo |work= Aviation Week |date= 21 July 2014 |first=Jens|last=Flottau|first2=Guy|last2=Norris|url-access=subscription}}</ref>\n<ref name=AN141125>{{cite news |url= http://airwaysnews.com/blog/2014/11/25/analysis-delta-order-for-a350-a330neo-hinged-on-pricing-availability/ |title= Delta Order for A350; A330neo Hinged on Pricing, Availability |work= Airwaysnews |date= 25 November 2014 |access-date= 30 October 2015 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151117045118/http://airwaysnews.com/blog/2014/11/25/analysis-delta-order-for-a350-a330neo-hin