0neo-specifics-450083/ |title= Airbus and United talk A321LR and A330neo specifics |date= 10 July 2018 |author= Edward Russell |work= Flightglobal}}</ref>\n| {{cvt|132|t|lb}}{{efn|proposed to United with 252 seats (51 first and business, 56 extra-legroom economy and 145 economy)}}\n| {{cvt|137|t|lb}}{{efn|proposed to United with 303 seats (57 first and business, 32 extra-legroom economy and 214 economy)}}\n|-\n! Fuel capacity\n| colspan=\"2\" | {{cvt|139,090|l|USgal}}, {{cvt|111,272|kg}}<ref name=TCDS/>\n|-\n! Maximum speed\n| colspan=\"2\" |{{cvt|0.86|Mach|34000|knots km/h|0}}<ref name=800specs/><ref name=900specs/>\n|-\n! Range\n| 8,150nmi / 15,094&nbsp;km\n| 7,200nmi / 13,334&nbsp;km\n|-\n! Ceiling \n| colspan=\"2\" | 41 450&nbsp;ft (12 634m)<ref name=TCDS/>\n|-\n! Engine (\u00d72)\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[Rolls-Royce Trent 7000]]-72\n|-\n! Thrust (\u00d72)\n| colspan=\"2\" | 324.0&nbsp;kN / 72,834&nbsp;lbf (takeoff)<ref name=TCDS/>\n|-\n|}\n{{notelist}}\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal|Aviation}}\n{{aircontent\n|see also= <!-- other related articles that have not already linked: -->\n*[[Competition between Airbus and Boeing]]\n|related= <!-- designs developed into or from this aircraft: -->\n*[[Airbus A330]]\n|similar aircraft= <!-- aircraft that are of similar Role, Era, and Capability this design: -->\n*[[Airbus A350 XWB]]\n*[[Boeing 787 Dreamliner]]\n*[[Boeing 777X]]\n*[[CRAIC CR929]]\n|lists= <!-- Relevant lists that this aircraft appears in. -->\n<!-- See [[WP:Air/PC]] for more explanation of these fields. -->\n}}\n\n==Notes==\n{{reflist|group=upper-roman}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|refs=\n<ref name=Challenges2011>{{cite web |url= http://www.challenges.fr/entreprise/20110623.CHA5751/airbus-devrait-remotoriser-l-a330.html |title= Airbus devrait remotoriser l'A330 |date= 23 June 2011 |work= [[Challenges (magazine)|Challenges]] |language= fr}}</ref>\n<ref name=TAP26nov2018>{{cite press release |url= https://www.tapairportugal.com/en/media/press-releases/Press-Release-